> x village
You can't see much from this distance, though you spot a couple of decently-sized buildings.  The whole place looks quaint and picturesque.
> x volcano

> x volcano
It looks so serene and peaceful, lying there all round and green and forested like one of your mother's famous broccoli gelatins.
