> drink wine

> drink wine
You take another healthy guzzle from the bottle.  You're starting to feel more confident.  And tough!  In fact, you feel like you could take on the world and lick it with one hand tied behind your back!  You're not scared of anything!
> n

> n
No wimpy little two-bit cave mouth is going to give you the business!  You swagger in.  Or maybe stagger in.
