You're standing at the top of a vast wall which stretches east and west until it disappears on either side into thick, impenetrable jungle.  The area around the gate has been cleared, allowing you to scout out the land on either side.   To the south, you see tall trees and a wide, crystal-blue river.  To the north the land seems harsh, more forbidding, the tree cover lower but also darker and denser.   You can see the path twisting away towards what looks like a village.  Further on, a volcano belches ash and magma into the sky.

