This living titan represents Vola, the Golanese goddess of war, fertility, and dangerous halls and foyers.   She's about thirty feet tall, made of solid gold, and has four arms, real emerald eyes, and a knockout figure.   She's standing waist deep in a pit trap, but doesn't seem at all bothered by it.
