> give doorknob to Vola
"Well, that's hardly--oh.  Oh, that's rather nice, actually."   She takes the doorknob and pops in into her mouth like a bon-bon.  "Mmm!  You know, these low-quality alloys go right to my pedestal, but is it worth it?  Absolutely."   She pats her stomach with a loud clang of metal on metal and then fixes you with another emerald glare.  "Now, what ELSE do you have for me?"
