> give music to Vola
"You offer THAT to the Unconquerable One?"  Vola sneers.  "See, that, that is just not good enough.  Try again.  Oh, wait, you can't, because I'm going to eat you."

She grabs you, tilts her head back, and drops you down her gullet, her lips clanging shut above your head with a metallic finality.

