This poor adventurer must have made it all the way through the shrine's traps and defenses, only to fall victim to Vola's wrath.   Looking at the departed soul, whose story might have been your own, you whisper a heartfelt prayer to the heavens that there's something useful in his pockets as you rifle through them.  You find his ID card, a sketch of the golden shrine chamber, and fifteen cents, all of which you take.

You also discover a brilliant electrum idol gripped tightly by the bony fingers.
