> x idol
This idol could be Vola's much littler sister, but instead of the goddess's haughty sneer, the round face is serene and welcoming, the plump lips curled in a mysterious smile.   "I would not give my power to a thief," they seem to say, "but I will give it to you, Jacqueline McBean, she who would be Jungle Queen."  You feel an overwhelming desire to TOUCH it.
> touch idol

> touch idol
As your fingers brush against the idol, you feel as if you're being pulled in all directions at once, your atoms slathered across the universe like so much peanut butter.  You are growing, expanding, your hands stretching out to encompass the world.  You have come to the end of the path you have been traveling since lo, earlier today, shedding your old self like so many molted feathers.  You are no longer a pale, flabby city slicker.  You are a pale, flabby Jungle Queen!

You are now the ruler of all you can see, and can step from one part of your domain to another at any time.  WARP TO any place in visual range in order to travel there!  Luckily for you, your majesty, this ability also works on pictures and photographs.
> warp to sketch

> warp to sketch
Focusing on the sketch, you stride forward, feeling the world twist and shift in a nauseating swirl of black and green.  It's a little like being squeezed out of a tube of toothpaste.  At least that's how you imagine it; you've done plenty of stuff you're not writing home to Mother about, but you've never actually been squeezed out of a tube of toothpaste.

With a pop, you emerge in the central chamber of the temple.  You're free!

You are now the Jungle Queen.   Where you go next is up to you.

